{"tid":271042,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國遊一問","createTime":"2017-06-04T18:05:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T08:31:23.000Z","uid":89814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7aec01a2807c5995c61a1e6f0dd17d6eb8840640","tid":271042,"uid":89814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:05:31.000Z","msg":"黎緊8月中想同女朋友一齊去曼谷 第一次去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無平價酒店介紹<br />\n去6日5夜<br />\n睇過air asiago 有幾間都唔錯 酒店連機票package 大概2500$一位 不過回程既時間就勁早... <br />\n想問有無邊到有啲平價機票同酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bb759d31bc2415ac8159d809dd8a919e4cf14a","tid":271042,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:06:49.000Z","msg":"日日留係曼谷？"},{"pid":"2b98c877c20408ddadb1f935769e3a958a33413a","tid":271042,"uid":89814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:09:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>日日留係曼谷？</blockquote><br />\n其實想去玩下大象啊 食下野 行下街 <br />\n聽聞好似曼谷都有水上活動同埋動物園？<br />\n小弟知識薄弱 希望各巴打幫手"},{"pid":"ac78c466413eaeeb4c2a28ab337826fe04d28aed","tid":271042,"uid":89814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:09:37.000Z","msg":"同埋 學生哥 budget 有限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab5e0a71563d2cc93a5dbbf82799cd829ccaf53","tid":271042,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:09:41.000Z","msg":"睇水門個邊既酒店"},{"pid":"8fcaf15caff1d974d330166d57c952670acf7be6","tid":271042,"uid":24044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"2500 包機票同酒店係差唔多"},{"pid":"670191c08107eeeba5a59977bef99bf7c9434a22","tid":271042,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:13:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>日日留係曼谷？</blockquote><br />\n其實想去玩下大象啊 食下野 行下街 <br />\n聽聞好似曼谷都有水上活動同埋動物園？<br />\n小弟知識薄弱 希望各巴打幫手</blockquote><br />\n有啲人會搵兩日去芭堤雅，建議你plan好大概既行程係咪日日都留係曼谷先訂酒店，機票就可以訂左先"},{"pid":"a0c3f9eea371304e8fbd1eeb495bbe1f958da1a4","tid":271042,"uid":89814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>2500 包機票同酒店係差唔多</blockquote><br />\n有個諗法係 由於回程既飛機係泰國朝早時間4點幾 咁我地飛之前果一晚就唔住酒店 check out左就寄存行李係酒店 到夜晚先拎走去機場等 <br />\n咁樣可唔可行"},{"pid":"e87b2223cb857eaae70a7d10f143261888eb2170","tid":271042,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:15:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>2500 包機票同酒店係差唔多</blockquote><br />\n有個諗法係 由於回程既飛機係泰國朝早時間4點幾 咁我地飛之前果一晚就唔住酒店 check out左就寄存行李係酒店 到夜晚先拎走去機場等 <br />\n咁樣可唔可行</blockquote><br />\n可行，但你4點幾機返到香港清晨，果日都要休息，變相要請多日假"},{"pid":"7ba7cb72fddd28443dfe412cbc196866a490cf74","tid":271042,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:16:56.000Z","msg":"skyscanner + hotelscombined 自己揾"},{"pid":"47f11efebf6098de26f956f637a6969840fe20ca","tid":271042,"uid":15948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:17:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2500 包機票同酒店係差唔多</blockquote><br />\n有個諗法係 由於回程既飛機係泰國朝早時間4點幾 咁我地飛之前果一晚就唔住酒店 check out左就寄存行李係酒店 到夜晚先拎走去機場等 <br />\n咁樣可唔可行</blockquote><br />\n可行，但你4點幾機返到香港清晨，果日都要休息，變相要請多日假</blockquote><br />\n學生哥"},{"pid":"ed526942980820b684f8436c2547bf572b150a1d","tid":271042,"uid":89814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T18:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2500 包機票同酒店係差唔多</blockquote><br />\n有個諗法係 由於回程既飛機係泰國朝早時間4點幾 咁我地飛之前果一晚就唔住酒店 check out左就寄存行李係酒店 到夜晚先拎走去機場等 <br />\n咁樣可唔可行</blockquote><br />\n可行，但你4點幾機返到香港清晨，果日都要休息，變相要請多日假</blockquote><br />\n學生哥</blockquote><br />\n都預左果日用黎休息 之後再去返pt"},{"pid":"36b9a8c8212832af1948edc85a2135687af2276f","tid":271042,"uid":91536,"like":0,